3. Required Software/Packages

	Package Name - Version built on
	------------------------------

	Python:
		bottle - 0.12.8 
		mysql-connector-python - 1.2.3
		pycurl - 7.19.5
		pyYAML - 3.11

	Java:
		JDK - 8.0_45


4. Installation Instructions

	Ubuntu:
		sudo apt-get install python python-pip python-bottle python-mysql.connector python-pycurl python-yaml mysql-server

		sudo pip install --allow-external -r dash_requirements_min.txt
			or
		sudo pip install --allow-external -r dash_requirements.txt
			or
		sudo pip install bottle
		sudo pip install mysql-connector-python
		sudo pip install pycurl
		sudo pip install pyyaml
 
